                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign>
                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word God is not rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works</desc>
                  <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#80r">fol. 80r</locus> (tenth biblical canticle)</desc>
                  </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#40v" facs="041">Fol. 40v</locus><desc>crude drawing of a figure</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#47r" facs="047">Fol. 47r</locus><desc>crude drawing of a face</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#50r" facs="050">Fol. 50r</locus><desc>crude drawing of a face</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#6r #10v #18v #28r #34r #60v #67v #72r #82v" facs="006 011 019 028 034 061 068 072 083">folss. 6r, 10v, 18v, 28r, 34r, 60v, 67v, 72r, 82v, </locus> (red and black haräg);
                    <locus target="#23v" facs="024">23v, </locus> (line of alternating red and black dots);
                    <locus target="#89r" facs="089">89r</locus> (line of red dots)
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <locus target="#23v" facs="024">Fol. 23v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    The midpoint of the Psalms is marked with a like of alternating red and black dots
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#102r" facs="102">Fol. 102r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Scrawls
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#102v" facs="103">Fol. 102v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Record including the date “in the year of John the Evangelist, 1924 EC.”<date calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1924">1924 EC</date>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <locus target="#103r #103v" facs="103 104">Fols. 103r, 103v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Scrawls
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus target="#2v #3v #4r #8r #10v" facs="003 004 004 008 011">Fols. 2v, 3v, 4r, 8r, 10v</locus>
                    <desc>etec., words of text are written interlinearly;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#8r #49r #75r #84v #96r" facs="008 049 075 085 096">Fols. 8r, 49r, 75r, 84v, 96r</locus>
                    <desc>etc., lines of text are written interlinearly;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <locus target="#92r" facs="092"> f. 92r, col. 2, line 3</locus>
                    <desc>
                    lines of text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (┬) marking the location where the text is to be inserted;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e7">
                    <locus target="#74r" facs="074">Fol. 74r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    erasure markings are visible;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e8">
                    <locus target="#10v #11r #52v #59v #77v" facs="011 053 060 078">Fols. 10v, 11r, 52v, 59v, 77v</locus>
                    <desc>etc., text has been removed
